description._content:
Date: 18 June 1946
Reference code: P581

Item is a group photograph of members of the Judicial Committee of the Privy Council on the occasion of returning to Downing Street for the first time since the premises were damaged by bombing on the 14th October 1940. Depicted are: M.R Jayaker, Lord Du Parcq, Lord Goddard (Lord Chief Justice), Lord Simonds, Lord Macmillan, Viscount Simon, The Lord Chancellor (Lord Jowitt), Lord Thankerton, Lord Porter, Lord Uthwatt, Sir Madhavan Nair, and Sir John Beaumont.
